                src="/narasumber/Oluwatoyin.png"
                alt="Oluwatoyin"
                name="Oluwatoyin Muse Johnson Popoola, JP, Ph.D., MBA PGDAF., HDipl., RPA., Member INSOL International., AM(M)., CFA., FCTI., FCA."
